## 10. App Store Compliance

### Apple App Store
- [ ] `ios.bundleIdentifier` set in `app.json` (reverse-domain format)
- [ ] `ios.buildNumber` set and incremented for each release
- [ ] `ios.config.usesNonExemptEncryption: false` declared (standard HTTPS apps)
- [ ] `NSUserTrackingUsageDescription` declared if any analytics used (ATT)
- [ ] Privacy policy URL set in `app.json` (`privacyPolicyUrl`)
- [ ] App icon: 1024×1024 PNG, no alpha channel
- [ ] Splash screen configured
- [ ] All NSUsageDescription strings set for any accessed hardware
- [ ] `eas.json` has `production` build profile
- [ ] TestFlight internal testing completed

### Google Play Store
- [ ] `android.package` set in `app.json` (reverse-domain format, no hyphens)
- [ ] `android.versionCode` set and incremented for each release
- [ ] `android.adaptiveIcon` configured
- [ ] `allowCleartextTraffic: false`
- [ ] All permissions justified — no unused permissions
- [ ] `app-bundle` build type set in production EAS profile
- [ ] Data safety form completed in Play Console

---
